{"tid":2024601,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"送頭論只會令人少 唔會冇人出","createTime":"2020-05-19T17:05:29.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-19T19:02:53.000Z","uid":149827,"like":27,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"9190e8adde069ed068e7848737a700a5a8703aeb","tid":2024601,"uid":149827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T17:05:29.000Z","msg":"我想講 <br />\n<br />\n612 朝早全部人都係非法集結 <br />\n但狗唔會大規模捉人<br />\n原因係因為人多 並唔係因為冇犯法<br />\n（只係講朝早 唔係講衝立會）<br />\n<br />\n係 今時今日係一定唔會當時咁多人<br />\n因為唔團結 每日都內鬥<br />\n兄弟爬山 已經變成笑話<br />\n<br />\n每次有行動前夕 都有好多人話係送頭<br />\n但熱心既人真係會留係屋企？<br />\n只會令和理非唔出 人就少咗 結果...<br />\n<br />\n冇錯今日啲狗係痴線好多<br />\n白色恐怖六月已經有 但冇效 <br />\n因為夠團結 每次都好多人 <br />\n包抄都係夜晚 人少咗 有人唔願走<br />\n但唔會有人氣餒<br />\n<br />\n今日 白色恐怖 加 連登風氣<br />\n成功令和理非變成 幫襯黃店變抗爭主線<br />\n<br />\n唔係想話街頭抗爭係主線 <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">但可唔可以唔好再講送頭呀</span><br />\n我知道有好多人唔想見到後生俾人打俾人拉<br />\n斷送前程<br />\n<br />\n無論邊一條線 都要唔同人既支持先行到<br />\n<br />\n527 無論點都好 <br />\n大家可唔可以幫下手<br />\n做路人都可能救到人<br />\n<br />\n但睇live 然後又放負話送頭既人<br />\n你係賣緊隊友 冇錯 我話既送頭論既人<br />\n<br />\n我講咁大篇野 其實都係唔想見到送頭論<br />\n其實我唔明同路人會講送頭呢個詞語<br />\n<br />\n香港人 團結"},{"pid":"2da34904d416295190a9eba941ece096b4ca05d7","tid":2024601,"uid":149827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T17:05:48.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"18206698dc3a4cb82694060b56a5b14e82552406","tid":2024601,"uid":149827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T17:06:02.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"269ee64aa69ff768108ace07eb16885b1a2d9855","tid":2024601,"uid":45123,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T17:06:24.000Z","msg":"由唔可以提送頭 到次次都係送頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4904c25f3b67f628234804cb0f6415560a54dca5","tid":2024601,"uid":149827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T17:06:26.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"70cd2db0dde2296e195a5c38324021dc33e0560f","tid":2024601,"uid":149827,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"269ee64aa69ff768108ace07eb16885b1a2d9855","tid":2024601,"uid":45123,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T17:06:24.000Z","msg":"由唔可以提送頭 到次次都係送頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T17:08:33.000Z","msg":"人多係會令風險減少<br />\n有行動係有問題 大家可以用理據 討論<br />\n但一下就送頭 咁咪人少 <br />\n但又一定唔會冇人出 咁咪變真送頭"},{"pid":"d7b3ef24e8e0d23d84977f79b04526ae0e5445cd","tid":2024601,"uid":149827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T17:09:26.000Z","msg":"我想討論下 送頭呢個詞語真係啱咩 ？"},{"pid":"ac705d24d25a363b414c9410f14c6b00bf13e08f","tid":2024601,"uid":149827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T17:09:48.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c141b691188dd1cda42693073dc555754adc7b4e","tid":2024601,"uid":139294,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T17:10:20.000Z","msg":"你咪試吓吹雞 今時今日仲有幾多個人會出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5fb84665301667ecec7209bbabc8cf2325500dc6","tid":2024601,"uid":149827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T17:10:53.000Z","msg":"同埋我指係大型既活動 <br />\n唔係快閃 快閃有快閃做法<br />\n<br />\n大型就一定要有人"},{"pid":"54235c453e47ca5e159f052449ca25cd773bf51f","tid":2024601,"uid":326261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T17:11:47.000Z","msg":"Up"},{"pid":"864b83b60fa4c39bf36b65a4162f40f35797af79","tid":2024601,"uid":326261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T17:12:29.000Z","msg":"冇行動係冇代價"},{"pid":"04cb80efc903cfeca893c98a4e4460898dc4b59b","tid":2024601,"uid":149827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c141b691188dd1cda42693073dc555754adc7b4e","tid":2024601,"uid":139294,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T17:10:20.000Z","msg":"你咪試吓吹雞 今時今日仲有幾多個人會出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T17:12:35